  "notes": "\u003cp\u003eThese API endpoints work with the new Alerts on alerts.newrelic.com.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eAlerts policies are rules that govern New Relic notifications for your: applications, key transactions,\nand servers. Notifications are triggered based on condition values, after given number of minutes, at two\ndifferent levels:\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThe alerts policies resource provides information about an account’s policy. It also allows for\nquerying policies.\u003c/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eSee our documentation for a discussion on using the REST API with\n\u003ca href=\"https://docs.newrelic.com/docs/alerts/new-relic-alerts/rest-api-alerts/rest-api-calls-new-relic-alerts#policies\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e Alert polices\u003c/a\u003e.\u003c/p\u003e\n",
